__SqlaTable__.sql: SELECT * FROM form_details ORDER BY date_added

SELECT CASE 
      WHEN stars = 1  THEN '1 star'
      WHEN stars = 2  THEN '2 star'
      WHEN stars = 3  THEN '3 star'
      WHEN stars = 4  THEN '4 star'
      WHEN stars = 5  THEN '5 star'
      ELSE NULL
      END AS stars, COUNT(*) AS count
FROM pizza_survey
WHERE borough != 'NULL'
GROUP BY stars
ORDER BY stars DESC
LIMIT 10000
